div.p:
43. Resident General broadcast speech yesterday evening which made following
                    point: immediate improvement of agricultural salaries; granting of syndical
                    rights; economic recovery; opening of public functions to young Moroccans;
                    apprenticeship in democracy for Moroccans in local and regional assemblies;
                    study of reorganization of central power in free Franco-Moroccan consultations;
                    creation of council of diverse political opinion to study reforms. Translation
                    by pouch.
